title: Sonic DVD Audio Creator 3.0.05
description: Sonic DVD-Audio Creator is the world's first, and only, full-specification DVD-Audio authoring workstation. Built on core technology from Matsushita (MEI), the benchmark standard for DVD compatibility and a long-time technology partner of Sonic, DVD-Audio Creator gives you fast and efficient access to every aspect of the DVD-Audio specification, allowing the speedy creation of pure DVD-Audio, complex DVD-Audio and hybrid DVD-Audio/DVD-Video titles. DVD-Audio Creator is an authoring solution for mastering audio, video and graphical elements prepared in complementary applications from Sonic
